<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Research Participation</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f4f7fb 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      color: #111827;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      padding: 56px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #e0f2fe;
      color: #0369a1;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #4b5563;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }

    .info-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 36px 0;
    }

    .info-card {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 22px 16px;
    }

    .info-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .info-card span {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 16px 34px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #111827;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.25);
    }

    .notice {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 42px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container {
        padding: 40px 24px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .info-box {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="container">
      <div class="badge">Research Survey</div>

      <h1>AI 광고 영상에 대한<br />소비자 인식 조사</h1>

      <p class="subtitle">
        본 조사는 AI로 제작된 기업 브랜딩 광고에 대한 소비자의 인식,
        신뢰도, 배신감, 추천 의향을 알아보기 위한 연구입니다.
        아래 버튼을 눌러 설문에 참여해 주세요.
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-card">
          <strong>소요 시간</strong>
          <span>약 3–5분 정도 소요됩니다.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <strong>참여 방식</strong>
          <span>광고 영상을 시청한 후 설문에 응답합니다.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <strong>익명 응답</strong>
          <span>응답은 연구 목적으로만 사용됩니다.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="button" onclick="goToSurvey()">설문 시작하기</button>

      <p class="notice">
        참여를 원하지 않으실 경우 언제든 페이지를 종료하셔도 됩니다.
      </p>

      <footer>
        © 2026 AI Branding Advertisement Research
      </footer>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    const surveyLinks = [
      "https://forms.gle/6Aoa49ETjemnkNL9A",
      "https://forms.gle/6ohNnLhfRucKeq8Z9",
      "https://forms.gle/UdoYgqebULh9gAiDA",
      "https://forms.gle/UpKA7uV19Pcx2eWg6"
    ];

    function goToSurvey() {
      let savedLink = localStorage.getItem("assignedSurveyLink");

      if (!savedLink) {
        const randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * surveyLinks.length);
        savedLink = surveyLinks[randomIndex];
        localStorage.setItem("assignedSurveyLink", savedLink);
      }

      window.location.href = savedLink;
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
